{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d3f720bccc","title":"第一次接见红卫兵时在天安门上同彭小蒙的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"916e6fe919","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"d3f720bccc"}],"tags":[{"id":"299424f798","name":"教育和教育革命","type":"主题"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3be4d5766f","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"971f7057a8","type":"title","text":"第一次接见红卫兵时在天安门上同彭小蒙的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"0de5921179","type":"paragraph","text":"第一次接见红卫兵时在天安门上同彭小蒙的谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"b15d91bc98","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"9e8a5df02f","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.08.18","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"25fade6b66","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：陆平现在干什么？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"f256c81b10","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：陆平在北大扫地。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"ff9e61251e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：陆平只能扫地，就象我一样，我到了你们学校也只能扫扫地，别的干不来。我是你们的勤务员。张承先也是个坏人，把你们“红旗”拆散了。你们要把“红旗”拉起来。你们发展了多少人呢？","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"6e9af3e0c8","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：有发展了。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"d0c766d389","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这就对头了。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"cf985c2e46","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：主席身体好不好？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"47847aa4ed","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我身体很好。我在长江里游泳，有个青年同志肝痛了，我就上来了，要不然可以游三、四个小时。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"deff4d3738","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：下一步怎么办？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"23ed018edd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们一斗二批三改，按十六条办事。会不会游泳？","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"29fe9411c5","type":"paragraph","text":"彭：才学会，游得不好，很乱。只会游十几米。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"82cb941e72","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那不叫游泳，那叫闲庭信步。（这时毛作了闲庭信步的样子）你要能这样，就从必然王国到自由王国了。你们老怕别人批评。马克思主义就是压出来的。经风雨，发展兴旺起来。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"3b8bb2d8dd","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不能让她老出风头，要让她谦虚。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"},{"id":"469a1fec19","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你怎么能这样说呢？要让人家干革命嘛！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc"}],"page":{"id":"3b5328ebd6","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d3f720bccc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}